General.Name: Zoom2u Technologies Ltd
General.Description: Zoom2u Technologies Limited develops technology solutions for last mile delivery industry in Australia and internationally. The company operates Locate2u, a software as a services platform that enables businesses to manage their deliveries ; and Zoom2u, a delivery platform that connects with local independent couriers for same day delivery. It serves consumers, small and medium-sized enterprises, corporates, and e-commerce businesses. Zoom2u Technologies Limited was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Pyrmont, Australia.
